                    <li>In addition, you can also provide a guest and a hotel as part of the data</li>
                    <li><U>NOTE:</U> If providing a guest, the guest email address must exist in the system. Please create a new guest by going to guest > create.</li>
                    <li><U>NOTE:</U> If providing a hotel, the hotel name must exist in the system. Please create a new hotel by going to hotel > create.</li>
                    <li>You can also use the 'Single Block Booking Example JSON' to upload a block booking.</li>
                    <li>You can also use the 'Mixed Block Booking Example JSON' to upload a block booking for a specific guest and specific hotel.</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
